name: Tezos Tale #09 - Death Thrall of Immortal
description: His yell could be heard all across the city, nay, the island, and the terrible words it whispered into each and every's ears was one of rancid, toxic beliefs, one of strife with neighbor, not for stances on human rights, but for who they are as a person; this putrid figure wanted even in death to dissuade those to his cause.
